---
title: Crispy Pancetta Tagliatelle with Black Pepper Pasta, Mushrooms and Thyme
description: Pancetta and mushrooms are great friends, and we think we've made the friendship even stronger with the addition of black pepper tagliatelle! A final dusting of zingy lemon zest is the finishing touch
